NETWORK MONITOR
======================

1. Setup
--- CONNAN ---
----------------------
Run conna commnand from build folder. Member to use " --build missing "
$ conan install .. --profile ../conanprofile.toml

--- CMAKE ---
----------------------

Running CMAKE will link the boost libraries and other dependencies using conan generated CmakeFiles 
$ cmake .. -GNinja -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release

- BUILD TYPES
$ RelWithDebInfo
$ Debug
$ Release

--- NINJA ---
----------------------
Run ninja to simply build a exe or some executable. This can be used to detect bugs during compilation
$ ninja


================================================================
CONAN
================================================================
- install conan using pip
1.  pip install conan
- update conan using
2.  pip install conan --upgrade